column2: # directions: First, read through existing descriptions and edit for accuracy. Then, fill out this column with a description of each file. Include information about what the file contains and why it's relevant to your data package workflow. Use full sentences (capital first letter and period at end). Try to avoid using commas (use semi colors or reword if possible). Spell out all abbreviations and acryonmns (e.g., "Fourier-transform ion cyclotron resonance (FTICR)" not "FTICR").
